      .accordion-inner
        %p Teiid 9.1 for Wildfly 10.0.0 is now <a href="http://teiid.jboss.org/downloads/">available</a>. The main features are:
        %ul
          <li><a href="https://issues.jboss.org/browse/TEIID-2715">TEIID-2715</a> <b>OData Metadata</b> support for providing the metadata extension properties for OData.</li>
          <li><a href="https://issues.jboss.org/browse/TEIID-4243">TEIID-4243</a> <b>BatchUpdateException</b> support in JDBC to indicate what part of batch succeeds when a failure occurs.</li>
          <li><a href="https://issues.jboss.org/browse/TEIID-4191">TEIID-4191</a> <b>NO QUOTE</b> option for TEXTAGG.</li>
          <li><a href="https://issues.jboss.org/browse/TEIID-4200">TEIID-4200</a> Moved to WildFly 10 as host environment</li>
          <li><a href="https://issues.jboss.org/browse/TEIID-4332">TEIID-4332</a> <b>Improved NDV</b> calculations for costing.</li>
          <li><a href="https://issues.jboss.org/browse/TEIID-4378">TEIID-4378</a> <a href="https://issues.jboss.org/browse/TEIID-4376">TEIID-4376</a> <b>Clob enhancements</b> to support concat and use in EXECUTE IMMEDIATE.</li>
          <li><a href="https://issues.jboss.org/browse/TEIID-4100">TEIID-4100</a> <b>OData expand</b> support for siblings and nested expands.</li>
          <li><a href="https://issues.jboss.org/browse/TEIID-4100">TEIID-4393</a> <b>Additional Geospatial Functions</b> to more fully support the SQL-MM specification.</li>
          <li><a href="https://issues.jboss.org/browse/TEIID-4421">TEIID-4421</a> <b>Embedded Translator Refinements</b> to allow for functioning that is similar to the server.</li>
          <li><a href="https://issues.jboss.org/browse/TEIID-3630">TEIID-3630</a> <b>Merge/Upsert pushdown</b> is now supported.</li>

